Title: Registration Office
Description: A facility engaged in various types of registrations, such as vehicles, houses and companies.

Title: Outdoor Area-Complex
Description: An establishment or area located outdoors. This is a base-level category that should be used for all places that do not fit other categories defined for Outdoor Area-Complex (900-9200-xxxx).

Title: Industrial Zone
Description: A non-residential area that is dedicated to manufacturing, industrial activities or storage facilities. This also includes business parks containing service industries.

Title: Marina
Description: A designated area that offers docking and other services for small boats, yachts, or pleasure craft.

Title: RV Parks
Description: A designated area that provides camping facilities for recreational vehicles.

Title: Collective Community
Description: A facility that provides an area for members to hold a common social, political, religious or spiritual events. For example, kibbutz, dojos, moshavs, agricultural communes, eco villages, art communities, convents, monasteries and housing cooperatives.

Title: Island
Description: A natural and geographical feature of land that is entirely separated by water from the mainland.

Title: Meeting Point
Description: A designated place where people can gather or must report to during an emergency (for example, tsunami, earthquake, fire, and so on).

Title: Building
Description: This is a plot of land that has a street number assigned to it. This is a base-level category that should be used for all places that do not fit other categories defined for Building (900-9300-xxxx).

Title: Residential Area-Building
Description: A building designated specifically for residential use.
